review:
I recently had the privilege of visiting Dr. Shireen Rashid's practice, and it was an outstanding experience from start to finish. 
When I walked into the clinic, the staff warmly greeted me. I didn't have to wait long before I was taken in for my appointment, which I greatly appreciated. Dr. Shireen Rashid is an absolute gem of a dentist. Their expertise and professionalism were evident throughout the entire visit. 
During the procedure, Dr. Shireen Rashid ensured that I was always comfortable and pain-free. One aspect that truly stood out to me was Dr. Shireen Rashid's commitment to patient education. They provided me with valuable insights into oral hygiene practices and preventive care, which I found incredibly informative and beneficial for maintaining my dental health in the long run.
